posting_body: ['NoHo Park West', '11311 Morrison St., North Hollywood, CA, 91601', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'Welcome home to NoHo Park West', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 875 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'NoHo Park West Apartments is located in the heart of the NoHo Arts District and a short drive from the studios of Burbank and the exclusive neighborhood of Toluca Lake.', 'Enjoy the proximity to the trendiest spots in San fernando Valley including dining, shopping and nightlife!', 'With great access to the 170, 134 and 101 freeways, NoHo Park West Apartments can take you anywhere you want to be!', 'Our one and two bedroom loft floor plans offer upgraded kitchens including dishwashers, stoves and garbage disposals as well as new light fixtures and washer and dryer hookups!', 'Live the good life at NoHo Park West!', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Friendly yes.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:1:00PM-3:00PM', 'j2tMNWidm']
